{"componentChunkName":"component---src-templates-post-template-js","path":"/2019/12/create-presentation-tool-from-scratch/","result":{"data":{"markdownRemark":{"id":"ae59c265-3fb9-52e4-9828-498a8019c5b4","html":"<!-- endExcerpt -->\n<h2 id=\"初识互动演示工具\" style=\"position:relative;\"><a href=\"#%E5%88%9D%E8%AF%86%E4%BA%92%E5%8A%A8%E6%BC%94%E7%A4%BA%E5%B7%A5%E5%85%B7\" aria-label=\"初识互动演示工具 permalink\" class=\"anchor before\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" focusable=\"false\" height=\"16\" version=\"1.1\" viewBox=\"0 0 16 16\" width=\"16\"><path fill-rule=\"evenodd\" d=\"M4 9h1v1H4c-1.5 0-3-1.69-3-3.5S2.55 3 4 3h4c1.45 0 3 1.69 3 3.5 0 1.41-.91 2.72-2 3.25V8.59c.58-.45 1-1.27 1-2.09C10 5.22 8.98 4 8 4H4c-.98 0-2 1.22-2 2.5S3 9 4 9zm9-3h-1v1h1c1 0 2 1.22 2 2.5S13.98 12 13 12H9c-.98 0-2-1.22-2-2.5 0-.83.42-1.64 1-2.09V6.25c-1.09.53-2 1.84-2 3.25C6 11.31 7.55 13 9 13h4c1.45 0 3-1.69 3-3.5S14.5 6 13 6z\"></path></svg></a>初识互动演示工具</h2>\n<p>参加过一次 <a href=\"https://www.gatsbyjs.org/\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"nofollow noopener noreferrer\">Gatsby</a> 线上讨论会，会后提问环节用 <a href=\"https://www.sli.do/\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"nofollow noopener noreferrer\">Slido</a> 互动收集问题，主持人解答了投票数最高的几个问题，当时这款 Slido 工具清爽得界面和简单实用给我留下很深印象。</p>\n<p><span\n      class=\"gatsby-resp-image-wrapper\"\n      style=\"position: relative; display: block; margin-left: auto; margin-right: auto; max-width: 760px; \"\n    >\n      <a\n    class=\"gatsby-resp-image-link\"\n    href=\"/static/a6893d04d9c88e158f1c01c3b1e3b73d/26178/event-pesent-mode.png\"\n    style=\"display: block\"\n    target=\"_blank\"\n    rel=\"noopener\"\n  >\n    <span\n    class=\"gatsby-resp-image-background-image\"\n    style=\"padding-bottom: 56.315789473684205%; position: relative; bottom: 0; left: 0; background-image: url('data:image/png;base64,'); background-size: cover; display: block;\"\n  ></span>\n  <picture>\n          <source\n              srcset=\"/static/a6893d04d9c88e158f1c01c3b1e3b73d/5ed05/event-pesent-mode.webp 190w,\n/static/a6893d04d9c88e158f1c01c3b1e3b73d/9d76b/event-pesent-mode.webp 380w,\n/static/a6893d04d9c88e158f1c01c3b1e3b73d/33466/event-pesent-mode.webp 760w,\n/static/a6893d04d9c88e158f1c01c3b1e3b73d/02ec0/event-pesent-mode.webp 960w\"\n              sizes=\"(max-width: 760px) 100vw, 760px\"\n              type=\"image/webp\"\n            />\n          <source\n            srcset=\"/static/a6893d04d9c88e158f1c01c3b1e3b73d/253c6/event-pesent-mode.png 190w,\n/static/a6893d04d9c88e158f1c01c3b1e3b73d/810ee/event-pesent-mode.png 380w,\n/static/a6893d04d9c88e158f1c01c3b1e3b73d/b4918/event-pesent-mode.png 760w,\n/static/a6893d04d9c88e158f1c01c3b1e3b73d/26178/event-pesent-mode.png 960w\"\n            sizes=\"(max-width: 760px) 100vw, 760px\"\n            type=\"image/png\"\n          />\n          <img\n            class=\"gatsby-resp-image-image\"\n            src=\"/static/a6893d04d9c88e158f1c01c3b1e3b73d/b4918/event-pesent-mode.png\"\n            alt=\"Slido 的提问互动演示界面\"\n            title=\"\"\n            loading=\"lazy\"\n            decoding=\"async\"\n            style=\"width:100%;height:100%;margin:0;vertical-align:middle;position:absolute;top:0;left:0;\"\n          />\n        </picture>\n  </a>\n    </span></p>\n<center>Slido 的提问互动演示界面</center>  \n<p>这类软件在国内多被称为“现场/大屏互动”工具，<a href=\"https://www.hixianchang.com\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"nofollow noopener noreferrer\">Hi现场</a>是这类产品的代表。这类产品功能丰富且贴近国情（微信、弹幕、摇一摇），同样界面也很接地气——眼花缭乱、纷繁复杂😵。我很不喜欢这种玩具化的界面，令人想起 2000年国内站长热时候的“<a href=\"https://museum.berlinchan.com/2003/08/16/star-land-v2/#%E5%8F%8D%E6%80%9D\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"nofollow noopener noreferrer\">网页特效</a>”，<strong>炫丽动感的界面吸引人们的注意力，反而降低有效信息传递的能力</strong>，甚至从心理上引导人们的思考方式，将严肃交流讨论的思维活动变成一场儿戏——<a href=\"https://www.zhihu.com/question/39259317\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"nofollow noopener noreferrer\">媒介即隐喻</a>。</p>\n<p>当然，就其本身定位用于娱乐领域，这并不是问题。后来找到一个面向国内的产品<a href=\"https://picpiclive.com\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"nofollow noopener noreferrer\">皮豆互动</a>还不错。</p>\n<h2 id=\"什么是互动演示工具\" style=\"position:relative;\"><a href=\"#%E4%BB%80%E4%B9%88%E6%98%AF%E4%BA%92%E5%8A%A8%E6%BC%94%E7%A4%BA%E5%B7%A5%E5%85%B7\" aria-label=\"什么是互动演示工具 permalink\" class=\"anchor before\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" focusable=\"false\" height=\"16\" version=\"1.1\" viewBox=\"0 0 16 16\" width=\"16\"><path fill-rule=\"evenodd\" d=\"M4 9h1v1H4c-1.5 0-3-1.69-3-3.5S2.55 3 4 3h4c1.45 0 3 1.69 3 3.5 0 1.41-.91 2.72-2 3.25V8.59c.58-.45 1-1.27 1-2.09C10 5.22 8.98 4 8 4H4c-.98 0-2 1.22-2 2.5S3 9 4 9zm9-3h-1v1h1c1 0 2 1.22 2 2.5S13.98 12 13 12H9c-.98 0-2-1.22-2-2.5 0-.83.42-1.64 1-2.09V6.25c-1.09.53-2 1.84-2 3.25C6 11.31 7.55 13 9 13h4c1.45 0 3-1.69 3-3.5S14.5 6 13 6z\"></path></svg></a>什么是互动演示工具</h2>\n<p>简言之，<strong>互动演示工具让演示者与其观众双向沟通</strong>。详细的介绍请参见《<a href=\"https://ahaslides.com/blog/what-is-interactive-presentation-software-and-how-should-you-use-it/\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"nofollow noopener noreferrer\">What Is Interactive Presentation Software And How Should You Use It?</a>》。</p>\n<p>还有不少 <a href=\"https://alternativeto.net/software/sli-do/\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"nofollow noopener noreferrer\">Slido 类似的工具</a>，功能大同小异，且国内都可正常访问，推荐大家使用。</p>\n<hr>\n<blockquote>\n<p>结合我常用的开发工具，从零开始创建一个以“简洁、易用、安全”为标准的多端互动演示工具，且叫它为 Askent，一个代号好记而已。好吧，既然又开始“造轮子”了，也不介意再造一个新词了😆，开始吧！</p>\n</blockquote>\n<h2 id=\"repository\" style=\"position:relative;\"><a href=\"#repository\" aria-label=\"repository permalink\" class=\"anchor before\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" focusable=\"false\" height=\"16\" version=\"1.1\" viewBox=\"0 0 16 16\" width=\"16\"><path fill-rule=\"evenodd\" d=\"M4 9h1v1H4c-1.5 0-3-1.69-3-3.5S2.55 3 4 3h4c1.45 0 3 1.69 3 3.5 0 1.41-.91 2.72-2 3.25V8.59c.58-.45 1-1.27 1-2.09C10 5.22 8.98 4 8 4H4c-.98 0-2 1.22-2 2.5S3 9 4 9zm9-3h-1v1h1c1 0 2 1.22 2 2.5S13.98 12 13 12H9c-.98 0-2-1.22-2-2.5 0-.83.42-1.64 1-2.09V6.25c-1.09.53-2 1.84-2 3.25C6 11.31 7.55 13 9 13h4c1.45 0 3-1.69 3-3.5S14.5 6 13 6z\"></path></svg></a>Repository</h2>\n<p><a href=\"https://github.com/BerlinChan/askent\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"nofollow noopener noreferrer\">https://github.com/BerlinChan/askent</a></p>\n<p>Working in progress, continually updated…</p>\n<p><a href=\"/2020/02/project-askent-admin-audience-client\">2月5日开发进度更新</a></p>","excerpt":"","fields":{"slug":"/2019/12/create-presentation-tool-from-scratch","categorySlugs":["/category/前端/"],"tagSlugs":["/tag/askent/","/tag/个人项目/"]},"frontmatter":{"title":"从零开始，创建一个多端互动演示工具","date":"2019-12-30T10:46:37.121Z","categories":["前端"],"description":"互动演示工具让演示者与其观众双向沟通。结合我常用的开发工具，从零开始创建一个以“简洁、易用、安全”为标准的多端互动演示工具。","tags":["Askent","个人项目"],"slug":"/2019/12/create-presentation-tool-from-scratch","featured_media":{"childImageSharp":{"gatsbyImageData":{"layout":"fixed","placeholder":{"fallback":"data:image/jpeg;base64,"},"images":{"fallback":{"src":"/static/621bac858be2847ce67a98ebe92a4854/e737e/askent-featured-cover.jpg","srcSet":"/static/621bac858be2847ce67a98ebe92a4854/e737e/askent-featured-cover.jpg 800w","sizes":"800px"},"sources":[{"srcSet":"/static/621bac858be2847ce67a98ebe92a4854/e7773/askent-featured-cover.webp 800w","type":"image/webp","sizes":"800px"}]},"width":800,"height":400}}}}},"prevPost":{"fields":{"slug":"/2019/12/common-problems-in-using-gnuPg"},"frontmatter":{"title":"使用 GnuPG 的常见问题"}},"nextPost":{"fields":{"slug":"/2020/02/project-askent-admin-audience-client"},"frontmatter":{"title":"互动演示工具 Askent 已开发出管理与观众端雏形"}}},"pageContext":{"slug":"/2019/12/create-presentation-tool-from-scratch","prevPostSlug":"/2019/12/common-problems-in-using-gnuPg","nextPostSlug":"/2020/02/project-askent-admin-audience-client"}},"staticQueryHashes":["2727970573","3709504828","4110059069"],"slicesMap":{}}